org.apache.spark.util.kvstore

接口 KVStoreIterator<T>

  • 所有超级接口:
    AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable, java.util.Iterator<T>

    public interface KVStoreIterator<T>
extends java.util.Iterator<T>, java.io.Closeable
    An iterator for KVStore.

    Iterators may keep references to resources that need to be closed. It's recommended that users explicitly close iterators after they're used.
